        title: 'Instant Activation',
        description: 'Get your drive away insurance activated instantly, allowing you to hit the road without delay.',
        icon: 'tabler:components',
      },
      {
        title: 'Affordable Rates',
        description:
          'Enjoy competitive pricing for short-term insurance, making it an economical choice for temporary coverage.',
